snippet.title: The Good and Bad of Demonetisation: How The Notes Ban Is Being Scammed

localized.description:
The Good and Bad of Demonetisation: Watch India TV's special report to know how note ban being scammed. Thousands of crores unaccounted money in denomination of Rs 2000, Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes have been seized across the country. Income tax department, ED, CBI, Police and IB are keeping eyes on suspicious transactions and raiding accordingly.
